These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, snooker, billiard
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, ferret, rabbit
1. the person playing snooker is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the lizard##2
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
4. the owner of the lizard is not the person playing snooker##6
5. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | billiard  | domino | snooker | backgammon  |
| Pet   | goat | ferret   | rabbit  | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
City: colone, boston, prague, london
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, writing, hiking, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
2. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
3. the person traveling to colone is the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to boston##2
5. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| City   | prague | boston          | london | colone     |
| Hobby    | hiking      | gardening | traveling | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bongani, bolivar, blend
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, snowboarding, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the bolivar-smoker##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
7. the blend-smoker is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | vegafina | bongani | bolivar     | blend |
| Sport   | tennis    | lacrosse   | surfing | snowboarding    |

