.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, photography, fishing, traveling
City: marseilles, rome, new-york, nizza
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | fishing   | photography         | traveling   | board-games    |
| City         | rome | nizza | new-york | marseilles |

