.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, baking, magic-tricks
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, tea, water
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is singing##7
2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
4. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
5. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person drinking lemonade##7
6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
7. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing   | baking | magic-tricks | chess    |
| Beverage         | 7up | water   | tea   | lemonade |

