.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, scooter, roller
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, horse, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
5. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
7. the person driving the roller is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Transport          | roller | jet-ski | bike  | scooter |
| Pet   | frog   | hamster         | horse | ferret |

