.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, german, french, turkish
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, hiking, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the german##8
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the turkish and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the german##8
6. the british is on the left or right of the french##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the british is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | german      | french | british | turkish   |
| Hobby      | chess | hiking | dancing  | magic-tricks |

