.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, american, canadian, egyptian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy, horror, western
1. the canadian is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
3. the american is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the american##7
5. the canadian is not to the right of the egyptian##8
6. the egyptian is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the canadian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Nationality     | american | canadian | egyptian | dutch     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | horror        | western          | comedy |

