.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero, crime, adventure
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, tea, juice
1. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
5. the person drinking 7up is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person watching crime movies is not the person drinking tea##6
7. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
8. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | fantasy | crime | superhero |
| Beverage     | juice | 7up       | sprite  | tea    |

