2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
3. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
4. the project-manager is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
5. the nurse is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
6. the accountant is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
