4. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
5. the baccarat-smoker is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
6. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
