.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, poker, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, architect, bartender, nurse
1. the nurse is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
2. the nurse is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8
3. the architect is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
6. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the bartender and the person playing snooker##7
7. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | snooker         | poker    | backgammon       |
| Job      | architect | nurse | entrepreneur | bartender |

