.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, lettuce, papaya, corn
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, journalist, architect, police-officer
1. the police-officer is not to the left of the journalist##8
2. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
3. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
4. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating corn and the architect##2
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
6. the chef is between the journalist and the police-officer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food   | cauliflower     | lettuce | corn        | papaya       |
| Job      | architect | journalist  | chef | police-officer |

