.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, writer, coach, musician
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, snake, hamster
 1. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 2. the musician is not to the left of the coach##8
 3. the lawyer is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the writer##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the lawyer is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the lawyer##8
10. the writer is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Job          | writer    | coach | lawyer | musician |
| Pet   | goldfish | hamster  | snake     | rabbit    |

