4. the owner of the goldfish is the palace house##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the colonial house is between the owner of the mouse and the palace house##2
7. the wooden house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
