.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, punk, reggae, gospel
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, apricot, light-blue
1. the person who likes blood-red is not the fan of rock##6
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who likes light-blue##8
4. the fan of reggae is the person who likes coral##1
5. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes coral##7
6. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of rock##1
7. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes light-blue and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | punk    | gospel | rock | reggae |
| Color   | blood-red | light-blue      | apricot     | coral     |

 